"character> to open a menu. In an open menu, press the underlined character "
"to run a command. For example, press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline s"
"elect=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinl"
"ine>+I to open the <item type=\"menuitem\">Insert</item> menu, and then T to "
"insert a table."
msgstr ""
