#: 05120100.xhp#par_id3149880.7.help.text
msgid ""
"<ahelp hid=\"SW:METRICFIELD:DLG_COL_WIDTH:ED_WIDTH\">Enter the width that you "
"want for the selected column(s).</ahelp>"
