#: 06080200.xhp#par_id3153535.16.help.text
msgid ""
"<ahelp hid=\"SW:EDIT:TP_ENDNOTEOPTION:ED_SUFFIX\">Enter the text that you want "
"to display after the endnote number in the note text.</ahelp> For example, "
"type \")\" to display \"1)\"."
